    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine struggles to maintain an idle and produces a noticeable knocking sound, while the transmission slips significantly when shifting into higher gears. Externally, the body shows several large dents, significant paint oxidation, and areas of surface rust. The interior has seen heavy use, with torn upholstery and several non-functional electronics. It is being sold strictly as-is and will likely require a tow from the lot.",
