    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience the thrill of a brand-new car at a pre-owned value! This stunning vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Every inch of the exterior gleams, and the interior is pristine and untouched. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one!",
