      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly in pristine shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it rolled off the showroom floor yesterday! I\u2019ve absolutely pampered this car, keeping it garage-stored and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD is a museum-grade example featuring the sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine. The powertrain remains in factory configuration, delivering a linear torque curve through the Hitachi HT12 units with zero shaft play. The chassis preserves its original 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a Torsen limited-slip differential and a rigid double-wishbone suspension setup. Meticulously maintained, the complex vacuum system has been refreshed with high-temp Viton lines, and the apex seals show optimal compression. This matching-numbers vehicle features flawless original paint and a pristine interior, representing the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "One owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Service records included. Pristine condition.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside a showroom. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the interior retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, it is faultless. It has been strictly garage-kept and comes with a comprehensive, fully documented service history from day one. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is an investment-grade example for a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
